updates.title: GPT-5.2 derives a new result in theoretical physics
updates.summary: A new preprint shows GPT-5.2 proposing a new formula for a gluon amplitude, later formally proved and verified by OpenAI and academic collaborators.

updates.title: Introducing Lockdown Mode and Elevated Risk labels in ChatGPT
updates.summary: Introducing Lockdown Mode and Elevated Risk labels in ChatGPT to help organizations defend against prompt injection and AI-driven data exfiltration.

updates.title: Beyond rate limits: scaling access to Codex and Sora
updates.summary: How OpenAI built a real-time access system combining rate limits, usage tracking, and credits to power continuous access to Sora and Codex.

updates.title: Scaling social science research
updates.summary: GABRIEL is a new open-source toolkit from OpenAI that uses GPT to turn qualitative text and images into quantitative data, helping social scientists analyze research at scale.

updates.title: Introducing GPT-5.3-Codex-Spark
updates.summary: Introducing GPT-5.3-Codex-Spark—our first real-time coding model. 15x faster generation, 128k context, now in research preview for ChatGPT Pro users.

updates.title: Gemini 3 Deep Think: Advancing science, research and engineering
updates.summary: Our most specialized reasoning mode is now updated to solve modern science, research and engineering challenges.

updates.title: Accelerating Mathematical and Scientific Discovery with Gemini Deep Think
updates.summary: Research papers point to the growing impact of Deep Think across fields

updates.title: Project Genie: Experimenting with infinite, interactive worlds
updates.summary: Google AI Ultra subscribers in the U.S. can try out Project Genie, an experimental research prototype that lets you create and explore worlds.

updates.title: D4RT: Teaching AI to see the world in four dimensions
updates.summary: D4RT: Unified, efficient 4D reconstruction and tracking up to 300x faster than prior methods.

updates.title: Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control
updates.summary: Our latest Veo update generates lively, dynamic clips that feel natural and engaging — and supports vertical video generation.
